The defendant Jennifer L. Lodygowski was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Jennifer L. Lodygowski is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Jennifer L. Lodygowski was found guilty of Drive or Operate Vehicle w/o Consent [Modifiers: Repeater], a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 943.23(3).
